@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_mxkzhm(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (((v2 + 0.74 * v1 + 0.24) / (tmp + 0.25 * v1 + 0.79)) + (0.51 / (v2 + 0.76 / v2 + 0.41)))
    v2 = (wp.abs(wp.cos(v1 + 0.07)) / v2)
    tmp = wp.exp(tmp)
    data[tid] = v0
